[{"location":"#OptimalBath","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath","text":"Documentation for OptimalBath.\n\n","category":"section"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.ForwardADGradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.ForwardADGradient","text":"ForwardADGradient(bathymetry::AbstractArray, β::AbstractArray)\n\nA gradient computation strategy using ForwardDiff for automatic differentiation. Stores two preallocated buffers: one for the bathymetry and one for the gradient results. The bathymetry starts as a copy of the initial bathymetry, and is updated during gradient computations.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.SinFVMPrimalSWEProblem","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.SinFVMPrimalSWEProblem","text":"SinFVMPrimalSWEProblem\n\nWrapper around SinFVM. Contains problem definition and solver parameters.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_flux_source-NTuple{4, Any}","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_flux_source","text":"compute_flux_source(Λ, Ul, Ur, Δx)\n\nComputes the source due to the reformulation of the adjoint pde to conservative form.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective","text":"compute_objective(U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, t, x, β, objectives::Objectives) where {S, T, N, A}\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient","text":"compute_objective_and_gradient(β, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, data::GradientData, ::GradientType)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_objective_and_gradient!","text":"compute_objective_and_gradient!(G, β, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, data::GradientData, gradient_type::GradientType)\n\nAssigns the gradient of the objective function with respect to the parameters β into G, and returns the objective function value.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.compute_Δx","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.compute_Δx","text":"compute_Δx(primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem)\n\nComputes the spatial discretization step size Δx for the given primal_swe_problem.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.create_callback","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.create_callback","text":"create_callback(f, primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem)\n\nCreates a callback function for the given primal_swe_problem that applies the function f(U_n::States, t_n, Δt) at each time step during the primal solve.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.get_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.get_gradient","text":"get_gradient(ad::ADGradient)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.get_objective","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.get_objective","text":"get_objective(ad::ADGradient)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.gradient!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.gradient!","text":"gradient!(ad::ADGradient, f, β)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.initial_state","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.initial_state","text":"initial_state(primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.objective_density","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.objective_density","text":"objective_density(obj::Objective, U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, I...) where {S, T, N, A}\nobjective_density(::Objective, U)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.objective_density_gradient","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.objective_density_gradient","text":"objective_density_gradient(obj::Objective, U::States{S, Depth, T, N, A}, I...) where {S, T, N, A}\nobjective_density_gradient(obj::Objective, U)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.solve_primal","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.solve_primal","text":"solve_primal(primal_swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, bathymetry, callbacks=[])\n\nSolves the primal shallow water equations for a given primal_swe_problem and bathymetry, returning the solution U, time points t, and spatial points x.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#OptimalBath.update_and_get_bathymetry!","page":"Home","title":"OptimalBath.update_and_get_bathymetry!","text":"update_and_get_bathymetry!(ad::ADGradient, swe_problem::PrimalSWEProblem, indices, β)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"}]
